Olakunle Churchill, the ex-husband to Tonto Dike, Nollywood actress, has gifted his ex-wife’s former friend; Blessing Osom, with the sum of three million naira in celebration of her birthday. Blessing shared the screenshot of the alert message on her Instagram page, as she received backlash from Nigerians over the act. While some accused her of being petty, others mentioned that she wasn’t worthy of the friendship in the first place. Follow us on Instagram and Twitter for updates. The post Olakunle Churchill Gifts His Tonto Dike’s Ex Friend 3Million Naira As a Birthday Gift appeared first on Olori Supergal. Source: Olori Super Gal